 </LayoutMultiFrame>
 <LayoutMultiFrame templateUuid="{225aa579-3a72-4b14-b71f-b2446373cfbe}" evaluateExpressions="true" url="" resizeMode="0" stylesheet="body { margin: 0 0;line-height: 122%;color: rgba(0,0,0,1.0000);font-family: Noto Sans, ;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;font-size: 14.6991px;text-align: center; }" type="65648" contentMode="1" html="&lt;p>The Geospatial Enabling Environments for Employment Tool (GeoE3), developed by the &lt;strong>World Bank&lt;/strong>, evaluates locations based on how supportive they are of employment and business opportunities.&lt;/p>&#xa;&#xa;&lt;p>By incorporating 15 spatial factors across three dimensions:&lt;/p>&#xa;&#xa;&lt;ol>&#xa;    &lt;li>&lt;strong>Contextual&lt;/strong>&lt;/li>&#xa;    &lt;li>&lt;strong>Accessibility&lt;/strong>&lt;/li>&#xa;    &lt;li>&lt;strong>Place Characterization&lt;/strong>&lt;/li>&#xa;&lt;/ol>&#xa;&#xa;&lt;p>GeoE3 offers a comprehensive analysis of how the environment impacts job prospects, indicating whether it is highly enabling or not enabling at all.&lt;/p>&#xa;" uuid="{225aa579-3a72-4b14-b71f-b2446373cfbe}" maxBreakDistance="10" useSmartBreaks="true" stylesheetEnabled="true">
  <childFrame templateUuid="{09aeb56e-778d-4793-8dd8-85781ae1e198}" uuid="{09aeb56e-778d-4793-8dd8-85781ae1e198}"/>
  <LayoutObject>
   <dataDefinedProperties>
    <Option type="Map">
     <Option value="" name="name" type="QString"/>
